Work Queue Flow

1. User clicks "Switch Work Queue" button
2. UserSwitchModalComponent opens with switchType: 'work-queue'
3. Modal checks: pageContext.getPageContext$('work-queue') 
   → Gets switched user name OR null
4. Modal determines effective user:
   → switchedUserName || currentUser.name
5. Modal makes API call: apiService.getTableData(effectiveUserName)
6. Modal updates work queue table data
7. Work queue shows the effective user's data

Case Management Flow

1. User clicks "Switch Case Management" button  
2. UserSwitchModalComponent opens with switchType: 'case-management'
3. Modal generates unique pageId: 'case-mgmt-1234567890'
4. Modal checks: pageContext.getPageContext$(pageId)
   → Gets switched user name OR null
5. Modal determines effective user:
   → switchedUserName || currentUser.name
6. Modal makes API call: apiService.getCaseData(effectiveUserName)
7. Modal opens new tab with case management data
8. New tab shows the effective user's case data
